videos.headline: South Carolina strikes first
videos.description: Jake Bentley connects with Shi Smith for a 38-yard score to give the Gamecocks a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Vandy punches it in for the score
videos.description: Vanderbilt RB Ke'Shawn Vaughn takes it in for a 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: South Carolina's 52-yard pass and catch sets up 2-yard TD
videos.description: Jake Bentley and Shi Smith connect for a big gain, and Rico Dowdle runs it in for a 2-yard score on the next play.

videos.headline: Vandy WR makes tough grab and stays in bounds for a score
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Kalija Lipscomb manages to hold onto the ball and stay in bounds for TD, play was confirmed after review.

videos.headline: Gamecocks' defense all over Vanderbilt
videos.description: South Carolina's Aaron Sterling recovers fumble to set up 1st and goal.

videos.headline: Goal-line run gives South Carolina 2 score lead
videos.description: Mon Denson fights his way into the end zone to give South Carolina 30-14 lead.

videos.headline: Gamecocks' RB goes up and over for score
videos.description: South Carolina's Ty'Son Williams leaps over the goal line for a touchdown.
